 program.\n\nNC leader Koirala also asked all to contribute their best to make the general convention of Nepali Congress successful at the previously scheduled time.","title":"Shekhar Koirala expresses concern on threat hovering over democracy - Khabarhub","url":"http://english.khabarhub.com/2020/28/145034/","video":[]}
